OL,3,CFive years to meet new limits on PFAS
OL,4,Cin water
OL,6,FNew limits for the levels of the
OL,7,Fforever chemicals PFAS are going to be
OL,8,Fwritten into Jersey's law and will
OL,9,Fhave to be met within five years.
OL,11,FThere are set standards for certain
OL,12,Flevels of chemicals and other
OL,13,Fsubstances which are already written
OL,14,Finto the 1972 Water law- this will
OL,15,Fensure PFAS is listed among them.
