OL,3,CFive years to meet new limits on PFAS
OL,4,Cin water
OL,6,FPFAS is a group of chemicals and they
OL,7,Fare not only found in water but in a
OL,8,Fwide range of everyday items,
OL,9,Fincluding cleaning products, water-
OL,10,Fresistant clothing, non-stick cookware
OL,11,Fand some beauty products like nail
OL,12,Fpolish and eye makeup.
OL,14,FPFAS do not occur naturally in the
OL,15,Fenvironment. Due to their chemical
OL,16,Fstructure, they are highly resistant
OL,17,Fto degradation processes and persist
OL,18,Fin water, soil and other environmental
OL,19,Fmedia over long periods of time. For
OL,20,Fthis reason, they are often described
OL,21,Fas "forever chemicals".
