OL,3,CFive years to meet new limits on PFAS
OL,4,Cin water
OL,6,FIt comes after Jersey's Independent
OL,7,FPFAS Scientific Advisory Panel advised
OL,8,Fthat a new limit of 4 nanograms per
OL,9,Flitre for the combined concentration
OL,10,Fof four PFAS substances in the islands
OL,11,Fpublic water be set. The most recent
OL,12,Fdata suggests the current level is 12
OL,13,Fnannograms per litre.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
