OL,3,CFive years to meet new limits on PFAS
OL,4,Cin water
OL,6,F"At present, there are no statutory
OL,7,FPFAS standards within Jersey's water
OL,8,Flegislation. These Regulations would
OL,9,Ftherefore establish the first legally
OL,10,Fbinding limit on PFAS levels in the
OL,11,FIsland's drinking water."
OL,13,FJersey water is currently running an
OL,14,F18 month trial looking at how best to
OL,15,Fremove PFAS from the island's water
OL,16,Fusing carbon. They are starting the
OL,17,Fwork in the laboratory before moving
OL,18,Fto the treatment works.
