OL,3,CFive years to meet new limits on PFAS
OL,4,Cin water
OL,6,FIn September, Jersey's health
OL,7,Fdepartment started offering islanders
OL,8,Ffound to have elevated levels of PFAS
OL,9,Fin their blood a type of cholesterol-
OL,10,Flowering medication named colesevelam,
OL,11,Fgiven its proven ability to reduce
OL,12,Fconcentrations of the 'forever
OL,13,Fchemical'.
OL,15,FThis was tailored towards those who
OL,16,Fmay have been exposed to chemicals
OL,17,Fwhich leaked into private borehole
OL,18,Fwater supplies after they were used in
OL,19,Ffirefighting foams at Jersey Airport
OL,20,Fin 1991.
